---
layout: base
title: Contact
permalink: /contact/
description: Get in touch with Mobius Integration — book a free discovery call or send us a message about your AI project.
---

<section class="bg-white py-20 px-4">
  <div class="container mx-auto max-w-5xl">

    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Let's Talk</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-xl mx-auto">Tell us what's slowing your business down. We'll listen, ask good questions, and come back with options — no pressure, no pitch.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Send a Message</h2>
        <form name="contactForm" method="POST" data-netlify="true" action="/thank-you-contact/" class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1" for="name">Name</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required
              class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-400" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1" for="email">Email</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required
              class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-400" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1" for="company">Company (optional)</label>
            <input type="text" id="company" name="company"
              class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-400" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-1" for="message">What's the challenge you're trying to solve?</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" required
              class="w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-400"></textarea>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-purple-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg hover:opacity-90 transition">
            Send Message
          </button>
        </form>
      </div>

      <div id="booking">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Book a Free Discovery Call</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">A 30-minute call where we map your workflow, identify opportunities, and give you a clear picture of what's possible — completely free, no commitment.</p>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200 text-center mb-6">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">📅</div>
          <p class="text-gray-500 italic text-sm mb-4">Booking calendar coming soon. For now, email us directly to schedule a call.</p>
          <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-purple-600 text-white font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:opacity-90 transition inline-block">
            Email to Book
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-gray-600">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-indigo-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <p>We'll walk through your current workflow and find the highest-impact opportunities</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-indigo-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <p>You'll leave with concrete ideas — whether or not you work with us</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-indigo-500 mt-0.5">✓</span>
            <p>No sales pressure — we'll tell you straight if AI isn't the right fit</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
